thread.title: Astros take 2-1 series lead over Royals with 4-2 win

title: Astros take 2-1 series lead over Royals with 4-2 win
text:
> Texas Astros take 2-1 series lead over Royals with 4-2 win Houston Astros' Luis Valbuena (18) and Chris Carter (23) celebrate after scoring on a single by Jason Castro (15) during the fifth inning in Game 3 of baseball's American League Division Series against the Kansas City Royals Sunday, Oct. 11, 2015, in Houston. (AP Photo/Richard Carson) The most compelling, sharable stories from across the web.
